results.titleNotTokenized: HPMA Conference: People Profession into the Future
paragraph:
SAP are proud to be supporting this years HPMA national conference. Once again the HPMA national conference will be virtual, on the Airmeet platform. This last year or so has certainly made sure that our NHS people services are as central to the workforce as our frontline services. Join us for the 2821 national conference to take a look at what the future holds for the people profession.

Join our breakout session on 2nd December at 1.88PM: How the NHS can support staff in times of crisis and develop a resilient workforce.

Now almost 2 years into the pandemic, the NHS & the healthcare workforce has been exposed to higher levels of stress than ever before. Supporting wellbeing is rising to the top of the priority list, but it can be challenging. What help is there for the NHS & healthcare organisations to better support their staff through difficult times & build resilience? We will discuss some of the ways these challenges can be reduced & the benefits to the healthcare workforce.
